text: Area 6 is probably my favorite Star Fox level ever. I almost wish future Star Fox games have levels that follow Area 6's example in its intensity and fun. Having to fight an entire fleet with multiple ships and advanced battleships was the best! The only other levels that can compare are some SNES Star Fox levels and the very first level in Star Fox Assault

text: Funny how this is my first Star Fox 64 upload, yet it's my favorite game in the series and easily the one I played most. Very fun game, I loved the tank so much I actually carved one out of wood during an art school project back then (I somehow lost it...). Miyamoto casually announced that Star Fox Wii U will be coming out next year before the next Zelda, so I'm greatly looking forward to that. Hopefully we get screenshots and videos soon.
